Hello,
We have 2 pipelines in photonvision with robotpy, one for april tags and one for retroreflective.
We can see targets for both on the web dashboard, but only april tag targets seem to be sent.
When we call self.camera.setPipelineIndex() and set it to 0,1,2,3 we don’t see any targets (except for april tags on index 2).

Any help would be appreciated-.

I don’t know anything specifically about how PhotonVision works, but the robotpy-photonvision wrapper hasn’t been updated to the latest version so that could be part of the issue. There is an open PR (Update to PhotonLib v2023.4.0 by auscompgeek · Pull Request #19 · robotpy/robotpy-photonvision · GitHub) but there outstanding issues that need to be resolved and nobody has stepped up to do so.
